Big Data 2015 - A Study of linguistic drift - Coverage of top K words - Gil Brechb√ºhler

This scala/spark code takes all the 1-grams and computes the percentage of the text covered by the top k% most used
1-grams.

/projects/linguistic-shift/topKWordsCoverage/" + percentOfTopWords + "-percent"

where percentOfTopWords is given as an input parameter.

A call sample :

spark-submit --class "NgramCoverage" --master yarn-cluster --executor-memory 4g --num-executors 200 target/scala-2.10/ngram-coverage_2.10-1.0.jar percentOfTopWords